      <species id="mw2475d92c_af35_4ab9_bab9_f6439217ccfb" name="qPSC" compartment="mwf09ac71b_d714_4cd1_99aa_defabb610f96" initialAmount="0" substanceUnits="MWUSERUNIT_cell" hasOnlySubstanceUnits="true" boundaryCondition="false" constant="false">
        <notes>
          <body xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Quiescent pancreatic stellate cells in tumor compartment. In normal pancreas, PSCs store vitamin A and maintain stromal homeostasis.</body>
        </notes>
      </species>
      <species id="mw4250a215_c004_4b15_84c6_446c4f857e37" name="iCAF" compartment="mwf09ac71b_d714_4cd1_99aa_defabb610f96" initialAmount="0" substanceUnits="MWUSERUNIT_cell" hasOnlySubstanceUnits="true" boundaryCondition="false" constant="false">
        <notes>
          <body xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Inflammatory cancer-associated fibroblasts. Secrete IL-6 and CCL5, driving MDSC recruitment and M2 polarization. Driven by tumor-derived IL-1alpha; TGFb antagonizes via IL-1R1 repression.</body>
        </notes>
      </species>
      <species id="mwe602a542_08d2_41a5_bf02_fd8f6d9311cf" name="myCAF" compartment="mwf09ac71b_d714_4cd1_99aa_defabb610f96" initialAmount="0" substanceUnits="MWUSERUNIT_cell" hasOnlySubstanceUnits="true" boundaryCondition="false" constant="false">
        <notes>
          <body xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Myofibroblastic cancer-associated fibroblasts. Secrete ECM, CXCL12, TGFb, VEGF. Build desmoplastic barrier. Favored by TGFb signaling (Biffi 2019).</body>
        </notes>
      </species>
      <species id="mw38864ae4_2e5d_4037_ba5a_0c5059617715" name="apCAF" compartment="mwf09ac71b_d714_4cd1_99aa_defabb610f96" initialAmount="0" substanceUnits="MWUSERUNIT_cell" hasOnlySubstanceUnits="true" boundaryCondition="false" constant="false">
        <notes>
          <body xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Antigen-presenting cancer-associated fibroblasts. Express MHC-II, present tumor antigen tolerogenically -&gt; Treg induction. Rarest subtype ~2-5% of CAFs (Elyada 2019).</body>
        </notes>
      </species>
      <species id="mw495fc6dd_7ebb_493a_a102_d254e705972b" name="collagen" compartment="mwf09ac71b_d714_4cd1_99aa_defabb610f96" initialAmount="0" substanceUnits="MWBUILTINPREFIX_milli_MWBUILTINUNIT_gram" hasOnlySubstanceUnits="true" boundaryCondition="false" constant="false">
        <notes>
          <body xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Fibrillar collagen (types I/III) in tumor (total mass in mg). Primary structural ECM component driving desmoplasia. Determines pore size (immune exclusion) and stiffness (mechanotransduction).</body>
        </notes>
      </species>
      <species id="mw145a61db_e302_41fc_a831_3cddc4ebd99b" name="CXCL12" compartment="mwf09ac71b_d714_4cd1_99aa_defabb610f96" initialConcentration="0" substanceUnits="MWDERIVEDUNIT_nanomolarity_milliliter" hasOnlySubstanceUnits="false" boundaryCondition="false" constant="false">
        <notes>
